      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like the interest is almost a hidden cost or something that's working against me on purpose. it's hard to feel like i'm actually making progress when so much is just swallowed up by the interest every single month. is there any way to minimize how much of that interest 'eats' my payment?",
